data.description: Check out this well maintained home on west side of town. This home has many updates that include, replacement windows, newer roof. new heating and air in 2019, remodeled bath, new gutter system in 2023.  It has a detached garage, a carport and a fenced in back yard. New vinyl on drive side of the house.   Don't let this one slip away. Call today for a showing.
